    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/1591"
                            >Benedicti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papê</rs> sede quarto, <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperatore</rs> domno <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/261"
                            >Courado</persName> agusto imperii in Italia anno nono, die duodecima
                        mensis decembris, indictione quarta, Prata. Petivi a vobis quidem in Dei
                        nomine <persName key="#Priests #Monks"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> per
                        iussionem a domno <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1574"
                            >Guido</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Linen #Pigs #Sheep #Operae #Levies #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie que vocatur a <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, una per consensum
                        deservientium eiusdem monasterii, me presente in Christi nomine
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes/de Berta">Iohannes qui vocatur de
                                Berta</name></persName> petitoris pro me et pro <persName><name
                                ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName> iugalis et pro <persName><name
                                ref="Vitaliana">Vitaliana</name></persName> relicta quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> petitoris in
                        tribus partibus et in quarta parte petitor <persName><name ref="Ursus"
                                >Urso</name></persName> filius quondam <persName><name ref="Vitalis"
                                >Vitalis</name></persName> nostrisque filiis et heredibus <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libelli</rs> nomine concedistis
                        nobis rem iuris supradicto monasterio vestro, idest omnes res et
                        pertinentias illas quantascunque nos abuerimus, que est posita in loco
                            <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Hay/fodder #Linen #Pigs #Sheep #Operae"
                            ref="#places/1574">Prata</placeName>, cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pascuis</rs>, <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs>sationalibus</rs>, una cum
                            <rs>arbustis</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs> et cum
                        omnibus sibi pertinentibus, constituta <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/3513"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/2424">Faventino</geogName></placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1490">Sancti Iohannis qui
                            vocatur in Axiata</orgName>; abendum, tenendum, cultandum, laborandum,
                        propaginandum, supersedendum, defensandum et in omnibus meliorandum, in
                        annis advenientibus viginti et novem ad renovandum; sub <rs key="#Levies"
                            >terratico</rs> de omni <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">labore maiore</rs>
                        modio quinto, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> quinto, minuto sesto, <rs
                            key="#Wine">vino</rs> anfora tercia, arbore pecto ponente semel; <rs
                            key="#Operae">brachiatico</rs> per omne canale corbe due de vino et
                        veturiam una adque redada una ad <rs key="#Levies">lignario</rs>; pro <rs
                            key="#Levies">glandatica</rs>
                        <rs key="#Pigs">porco</rs> uno si porcos abuerimus et si porcos non
                        abuerimus dare vobis debeamus denariorum Veneticorum solidi tres et omnes
                        asumptione sancte Marie cun uno nostro vicinum <rs key="#Sheep">pecora</rs>
                        una, aducto per nos in civitatem Ravenne, in domo vestra, cum fide et
                        puritate seu umilitate, sine dolo vel fraude aut malum ingenium; et non
                        abeamus licentiam tritulare neque vindimiare sine iussione domnica vestro.
                        Maiore quidem domnica vestra vel vestra dominatione cum onore et obedientiam
                        susipere debeamus et subceptionem eis facere. Pro eo quia accepistis
                        calciarii nomine, idest <rs key="#Clothings">froco</rs> una pro denariorum
                        Veneticorum libras quatuor. Si quis vero pars nostrum contra anc paginam
                        petitionem ire tentaverimus antequam finitum tempus sicut supra legitur, det
                        pars partis fidem servantis ante omnes litis initium aut interpellatione
                        pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">auri uncie due</rs> et post pene solutionis
                        manead petitio firma. Aldortinus per Domini misericordiam tabularius
                        scribendum rogavimus, sub die, mense et indictione supradicta quarta, Prata.
                        Signum manibus nostris supradicto Iohannes et Vitaliana et Urso anc paginam
                        petitionis ut supra legitur a nobis facta subscripsimus.</ab>
